# Deployment Environment Configuration Templates

## ⚠️ IMPORTANT: NEVER commit these .env files to git!

---

## Backend - .env.production

```
# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=production

# Database Connection (Supabase PostgreSQL)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://[user]:[password]@[host]:[port]/[database]

# Direct DB Connection for Prisma migrations (use Supabase direct host:5432, not pooler)
DIRECT_URL=postgresql://[user]:[password]@db.[project-ref].supabase.co:5432/postgres

# JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key_here_must_be_at_least_32_characters_for_security
JWT_EXPIRE=7

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# CORS Configuration
CORS_ORIGIN=https://is-prd-fs1.vercel.app

# Port (Render will set this, but providing as backup)
PORT=3000

# Optional: Payment Gateway (Razorpay)
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_secret
```

---

## Frontend - .env.production.local

```
# Backend API URL (Render deployment)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://is-prd-fs1-backend.onrender.com/api

# Supabase Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[your-project].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Optional: Analytics
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=
```

